comments: O'Neale (UTA) and Murray (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Gobert (UTA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Conley (UTA) swipes down and avoids making contact to Murray's (DEN) arm at the end of his drive.
Murray (DEN) briefly places a hand on Mitchell's (UTA) front, but Mitchell moves through the marginal contact.
Harris (DEN) places a hand/arm to the front of Mitchell (UTA) during the drive but the contact is marginal.
Plumlee (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Gobert (UTA) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Plumlee (DEN) makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) head/face during his catch and finish shot attempt near the rim.
A timeout was granted to DEN by the slot official prior to the inbound attempt by Plumlee (DEN).
Harris (DEN) and Murray (DEN) both reach in and make contact with the ball while and avoid making contact to O'Neale's (UTA) arms.
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal pivot foot as he calls for and is granted a timeout.
Harris (DEN) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it from Mitchell (UTA) during his drive.
After gathering the rebound, Gobert (UTA) turns to dribble and his left foot steps out of bounds.
Murray (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Conley's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
